# Node — after clone or `npm install -g`, dependencies live here locally only.
# Root package-lock.json MUST stay committed (not ignored) so `npm ci` and npm
# installs resolve the same tree as published versions (e.g. elkjs, js-yaml for
# `apltk architecture`).
node_modules/
